entries.allies_arrived: Your TIE Bombers have arrived, finish the job.
entries.allies_remain: Imperial Pilot: < Too much damage! I can't hold it together, ejec... >
entries.allies_win: Good, my faith in your abilities proved right. Return to me young one.
entries.enemies_arrived: Let the Rebels know what the war machine of the Empire is capable of. Destroy them all.
entries.enemies_remain: Imperial Squadron Leader: < Transport destroyed. %DI more to go. >
entries.enemies_win: It would appear my trust in your abilities was misplaced. Return immediately.
entries.found_loc: The TIE Bomber squadron will be at this location. Proceed there immediately.
entries.quest_findbattle_d: Proceed to these coordinates and meet up with the TIE Bomber squadron assigned to destroy the Rebel troop transports.
entries.quest_helpallies_d: Lord Vader has put you in command of the attack. You best not disappoint him.
entries.quest_location_d: The Kashyyyk system is not heavily controlled by any force. Beware of pirates, over ambitious slavers and in this case, Rebels.
entries.title: Kashyyyk system: Finishing the job.
entries.title_d: The Rebel Alliance is moving a fleet of troops to the planet of Kashyyyk in an attempt to liberate it from slavery and Imperial influence. Lead a fleet of Imperial fighters to first breach through the Rebel fighter defense and then to destroy the troop transports.
